titles: The Rota, or, News from the common-wealths-mens club written by Henry Stubb.
author: Stubbe, Henry, 1632-1676.
notes: A satire in verse ridiculing members of the Rota and the theories set forth in James Harrington's "The Rota, or, A model of a free-state or equall common-wealth."
Reproduction of original in the Harvard University Library.
